Description: Provides adaptive trend estimation, cycle detection, Fourier harmonic 
    selection, bootstrap confidence intervals, change-point detection, and 
    rolling-origin forecasting. Supports LOESS, GAM, and GAMM models, and 
    automatically handles irregular sampling using the Lombâ€“Scargle periodogram. 
    Designed for biomedical, environmental, and engineering time-series analysis.
